1
00:00:50,159 --> 00:00:51,439
(People say)

2
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:54,079
(it's better to miss than to meet.)

3
00:00:55,359 --> 00:00:57,600
(When he plotted against my kingdom
and betrayed my deep love,)

4
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:04,000
(I was Mu Ruyi, Princess of Xiling.)

5
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:07,719
(When he murdered my family
and shattered my homeland,)

6
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:11,879
(I was Jing Liuli, the resentful
court singer forced into this game.)

7
00:01:14,799 --> 00:01:16,319
(After love and hate burned to ashes)

8
00:01:17,239 --> 00:01:18,680
(and memory clouded my judgment,)

9
00:01:19,519 --> 00:01:21,319
(I was Liu Rushi, stepping once more
into the agony of love.)

10
00:01:22,319 --> 00:01:23,719
(In this life, across three lifetimes,)

11
00:01:24,519 --> 00:01:25,200
(it's fate,)

12
00:01:26,040 --> 00:01:26,840
(misfortune,)

13
00:01:27,519 --> 00:01:28,200
(resentment,)

14
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:29,879
(and hatred.)

15
00:01:31,159 --> 00:01:33,040
(In the end,
if we are destined to meet again,)

16
00:01:33,959 --> 00:01:35,400
(I will accompany you with my life)

17
00:01:36,239 --> 00:01:37,799
(and rush to you with my heart.)

18
00:01:37,820 --> 00:01:41,820
=Endless Love=

19
00:01:41,820 --> 00:01:44,740
=Episode 1=

20
00:01:44,820 --> 00:01:50,300
(Three months ago
by the riverside in Xiling)

21
00:01:52,719 --> 00:01:53,400
(Father,)

22
00:01:54,239 --> 00:01:55,000
(is this)

23
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,200
(the fate)

24
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:58,400
(of the Mu clan of Xiling?)

25
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,959
(If the curse of Butterfly Seal holds,)

26
00:02:01,020 --> 00:02:02,300
(Ancestral tablet of Mu Qiming)

27
00:02:02,319 --> 00:02:03,799
(it becomes my death warrant.)

28
00:02:04,799 --> 00:02:06,480
(Even with royal power and wealth,)

29
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,560
(I cannot escape from death.)

30
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:12,120
(Only the heart-blood of a beloved one
can break it.)

31
00:02:12,879 --> 00:02:15,479
(Deep love finds no good ending.)

32
00:02:16,039 --> 00:02:18,479
(How will my fate be resolved?)

33
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:20,599
(Where will it lead?)

34
00:02:55,599 --> 00:02:56,479
There's no one in the river.

35
00:02:56,879 --> 00:02:58,159
Why are you drowning here?

36
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,919
I am a slave of Xiling.

37
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:02,400
My family was slaughtered
by the Dongqing army.

38
00:03:02,719 --> 00:03:04,800
I was captured and brought here alone.

39
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,199
As I was unable to bear the humiliation,

40
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,759
I tried to escape through the waterway.

41
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,879
I am so grateful to you, heroic lady,
for saving me.

42
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,800
I have no intention of
offense or disrespect.

43
00:03:14,039 --> 00:03:15,759
If you are willing to show your mercy,

44
00:03:16,439 --> 00:03:17,800
then please just pretend
you never saw me

45
00:03:18,319 --> 00:03:19,039
and set me free.

46
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:22,100
(Slave)

47
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,599
What reason do I have to trust you?

48
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:28,439
If you refuse my request,

49
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:31,159
I have no reason to keep breathing.

50
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,479
I beg you,

51
00:03:35,159 --> 00:03:36,319
make it quick.

52
00:03:43,639 --> 00:03:45,120
I stabbed you once,

53
00:03:45,919 --> 00:03:47,080
but also saved you.

54
00:03:49,759 --> 00:03:50,680
Your body,

55
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,439
your heart,

56
00:03:54,159 --> 00:03:54,759
and your life

57
00:03:54,879 --> 00:03:56,800
all belong to me.

58
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:57,879
Your Highness,

59
00:03:59,039 --> 00:04:01,240
I am nothing but a lowly wretch.

60
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:04,000
Don't bargain with me.

61
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:10,719
Your Highness.

62
00:04:15,639 --> 00:04:16,680
- Let me go!
- Hurry!

63
00:04:17,879 --> 00:04:18,720
Spare me!

64
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,199
Your Majesty, please!

65
00:04:22,399 --> 00:04:24,040
Have mercy, Your Majesty!

66
00:04:31,399 --> 00:04:32,040
Stop!

67
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:37,120
Bring the heart-blood

68
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,800
and have the Princess consume it.

69
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:41,759
Mother,

70
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,519
it's only fleshly pleasure with them,

71
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:44,560
not true affection.

72
00:04:45,439 --> 00:04:46,360
Now you're doing this,

73
00:04:46,639 --> 00:04:47,480
it's only murdering the innocent

74
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,560
and a waste of your efforts.

75
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,000
This is my own life.

76
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:52,360
I don't want it stained
with any innocent blood.

77
00:04:53,959 --> 00:04:54,879
How can their lives

78
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:57,759
be compared to yours?

79
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,560
Then what about Father's life?

80
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,680
Is that the same?

81
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,600
If you indulge in earthly love,

82
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,199
how can you ascend to

83
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:08,879
the throne of Xiling?

84
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,279
This

85
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,319
is your fate.

86
00:05:15,879 --> 00:05:16,360
Mother,

87
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:19,040
I will not become another you.

88
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,959
And the one I choose to love

89
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:24,279
will not become another Father.

90
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:29,759
Make it known to all,

91
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,639
from this day, I will choose a husband,

92
00:05:32,120 --> 00:05:33,360
selecting the virtuous and refined

93
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:34,800
as my consort.

94
00:05:35,319 --> 00:05:36,560
Proclaim to Heaven and Earth,

95
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:38,680
together, we uphold
the royal ancestral temple.

96
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,480
Xia Ke'er.

97
00:05:44,879 --> 00:05:46,319
(Lanpingmei)
Do you think reading these dirty books

98
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:47,839
will really help?

99
00:05:48,759 --> 00:05:51,839
Days ago,
you made a solemn vow in the hall,

100
00:05:51,879 --> 00:05:53,800
confidently announcing
your husband selection plan.

101
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:56,079
(Xia Ke'er, General of the Xiling)
Now the Queen made all the arrangements.

102
00:05:56,199 --> 00:05:58,240
Countless men have entered the palace
to try their luck.

103
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,879
It's the Princess's husband.

104
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,439
If such good fortune

105
00:06:01,839 --> 00:06:03,040
could come

106
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:05,199
to someone precisely and suddenly,

107
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,560
they would be overjoyed.

108
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,639
Bragging feels great in the moment.

109
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:10,360
How do I tell?

110
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,560
How do I choose?

111
00:06:11,879 --> 00:06:14,120
Back when you held
your coming-of-age ritual,

112
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:17,240
those men flooded your mansion.

113
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:19,480
You injured hundreds at the scene.

114
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:22,279
Those matchmakers who tried to
arrange marriages for you,

115
00:06:22,439 --> 00:06:23,519
they became nuns one after another.

116
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:26,160
Even the holy monks
who came to counsel you

117
00:06:26,319 --> 00:06:27,399
returned to secular life at the scene.

118
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,759
Since then,

119
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,439
about your marriage,

120
00:06:31,399 --> 00:06:32,519
no one has dared to mention it again.

121
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:34,360
So you also think
I'm not fit to get married?

122
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,439
Not at all.

123
00:06:36,879 --> 00:06:39,920
You surely haven't met your Mr. Right.

124
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:42,160
I think we should just forget it.

125
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,079
It's not easy to meet one.

126
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:45,839
I'll wait for two more years.

127
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:48,680
When the Butterfly Seal strikes,

128
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,759
it won't be two years,

129
00:06:51,079 --> 00:06:51,920
two days,

130
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,839
two hours,

131
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:53,759
or even two blinks.

132
00:06:53,839 --> 00:06:55,680
You can't even wait for the time
of two slaps.

133
00:06:56,319 --> 00:06:58,360
The Princess's husband selection plan
starts now.

134
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,360
Gentlemen,

135
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:03,800
you have passed the fitness exam

136
00:07:04,279 --> 00:07:05,680
and the chastity exam,

137
00:07:06,199 --> 00:07:08,279
which means you are the finest
among the selected.

138
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,399
All gentlemen, hear my command.

139
00:07:09,639 --> 00:07:10,959
Show your best skills

140
00:07:11,079 --> 00:07:12,439
to me right now.

141
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,319
Let me see

142
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,639
that on the battlefield,

143
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,319
well, in the bedchamber,

144
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,560
what you're made of.

145
00:07:23,199 --> 00:07:25,680
How can you fight with
a build like a rake?

146
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:26,480
Get out!

147
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:30,560
You can barely even eat, can you?

148
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:31,920
Out!

149
00:07:33,279 --> 00:07:33,959
Your Highness, look.

150
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,480
These shortlisted candidates

151
00:07:36,759 --> 00:07:38,360
are all tough men to fight a war.

152
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,759
Are you picking a husband for me

153
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,879
or just picking ugly men to disgust me?

154
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:45,680
How about this?

155
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,600
Send these elite soldiers

156
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,160
to your mansion instead.

157
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,439
Thank you, Your Highness.

158
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:55,199
I will continue to work hard
and find your husband.

159
00:07:58,439 --> 00:07:59,240
Embroidery

160
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:01,240
is a man's best dowry.

161
00:08:01,720 --> 00:08:04,120
If a man cultivates both inner
and outer skills

162
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,360
with exquisite craftsmanship,

163
00:08:05,720 --> 00:08:07,199
he could certainly serve you well.

164
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,360
Look,

165
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,279
this man has remarkable skills.

166
00:08:12,480 --> 00:08:14,120
Even the tiny water droplets

167
00:08:14,199 --> 00:08:15,439
are vividly embroidered.

168
00:08:16,439 --> 00:08:17,560
But it seems

169
00:08:17,759 --> 00:08:19,800
these white patterns have no stitches.

170
00:08:20,759 --> 00:08:22,120
Your Highness, General,
I beg your forgiveness.

171
00:08:22,439 --> 00:08:25,000
These white marks are actually my rouge

172
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,519
mixing with my sweat.

173
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:29,360
They stained the embroidery by accident.

174
00:08:29,639 --> 00:08:31,399
You put on too much rouge.

175
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,440
Did you buy it by the cartload?

176
00:08:39,879 --> 00:08:41,279
Oh dear.

177
00:08:41,279 --> 00:08:42,559
What's wrong with you?

178
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:44,600
The needle pierced the silk,

179
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:48,519
and I feel sorrow for this silk.

180
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:50,840
Hold it.

181
00:08:51,399 --> 00:08:51,919
Guards,

182
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:56,399
send these men to General Xia's mansion.

183
00:08:57,279 --> 00:08:58,440
No, Your Highness!

184
00:08:58,759 --> 00:09:00,200
You want to give the ones
you don't want to me?

185
00:09:02,039 --> 00:09:03,480
The Princess hasn't come for days.

186
00:09:04,159 --> 00:09:05,080
Indeed.

187
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,279
Ever since I entered the palace,

188
00:09:06,519 --> 00:09:07,720
I haven't seen her.

189
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:08,240
Indeed.

190
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:09,519
If it weren't for the Princess,

191
00:09:09,879 --> 00:09:11,200
you'd be dead already.

192
00:09:12,919 --> 00:09:13,559
Here's your medicine.

193
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:14,559
Granted by the Princess.

194
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,279
You'd better think about

195
00:09:16,519 --> 00:09:17,720
how to repay the Princess.

196
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:20,759
May I ask where the Princess is now?

197
00:09:21,279 --> 00:09:22,879
The Princess is extremely busy.

198
00:09:23,039 --> 00:09:24,399
You can't see her whenever you want.

199
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,159
Indeed.

200
00:09:27,679 --> 00:09:28,960
How did all of you come here?

201
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,120
When I was picking herbs on the hill,

202
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,519
I slipped and fell down the slope.

203
00:09:31,519 --> 00:09:32,799
The Princess saved my life.

204
00:09:33,159 --> 00:09:35,159
I was robbed by thugs in the market,

205
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,320
and the Princess saved me.

206
00:09:36,639 --> 00:09:37,480
The Princess is truly valiant.

207
00:09:37,559 --> 00:09:38,759
The Princess is obsessed with
night hunting.

208
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:39,879
When might she

209
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,360
pay us a visit?

210
00:09:42,399 --> 00:09:44,360
May I ask where I can find the Princess?

211
00:09:44,759 --> 00:09:46,480
I wish to seek her counsel.

212
00:09:47,980 --> 00:09:49,420
(Slave)

213
00:09:51,120 --> 00:09:53,000
So he's the most wretched slave.

214
00:09:53,799 --> 00:09:55,519
How dare you seek the Princess's favor?

215
00:09:55,879 --> 00:09:57,840
Dream on!

216
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:00,840
What I despise most

217
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:03,799
are losers who trade on their looks.

218
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,120
What do you think you are?

219
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:08,639
You are not capable of
seeing the Princess,

220
00:10:09,159 --> 00:10:10,360
so you want to take it out on me?

221
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:13,360
It's better to improve your talents
and skills

222
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:17,279
rather than barking and biting here.

223
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:19,080
Tongue like a dagger.

224
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,720
I'll tear your mouth apart.

225
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,679
What I have in here

226
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,480
has no smell or taste,

227
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:30,679
the Gut-wrencher.
You'll never see it coming.

228
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:33,200
If you touch one drop of it by accident,

229
00:10:34,039 --> 00:10:36,240
you will bleed all over and die.

230
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,279
I don't believe it.

231
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:39,080
Slaves like me fear no death,

232
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:41,720
and I'm best at trading life for life.

233
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:44,440
Spare me!

234
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:45,559
Please have mercy.

235
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,720
I'll never mess with you again!

236
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,840
Never again.

237
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:50,679
I'll never do it again.

238
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,240
How crude he is!

239
00:10:54,399 --> 00:10:55,000
He...

240
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,279
He drank it.

241
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:57,440
You tricked me?

242
00:10:59,519 --> 00:11:00,600
Despicable wretch,

243
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,919
I'll kill you.

244
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:05,000
Your Highness.

245
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:05,799
Your Highness.

246
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:06,320
Your Highness.

247
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,879
I hate those who stir up trouble

248
00:11:07,879 --> 00:11:08,960
and cause disasters.

249
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:09,720
Guards.

250
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:11,000
Drag him out.

251
00:11:12,080 --> 00:11:14,200
This man shall never enter Ruyi Palace
in the future.

252
00:11:14,399 --> 00:11:15,480
Your Highness, I am innocent.

253
00:11:15,679 --> 00:11:17,000
Show your mercy, Princess!

254
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:17,399
Move!

255
00:11:17,399 --> 00:11:18,799
- He framed me! Your Highness!
- Move it!

256
00:11:18,919 --> 00:11:20,720
Please see clearly, Your Highness!

257
00:11:23,679 --> 00:11:24,639
You...

258
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,480
You're not as simple as you appear.

259
00:11:30,879 --> 00:11:31,720
It seems

260
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,879
I don't know you well enough.

261
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:38,000
Just some means of self-protection.

262
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:39,759
In this vast palace,

263
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,320
I act this way

264
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:44,279
only to have a chance to see you.

265
00:11:55,639 --> 00:11:57,240
I am but a lowly man.

266
00:11:58,440 --> 00:12:00,919
Your Highness need not trouble yourself
to bring the medicine.

267
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:12,919
You tried to approach me a few times.

268
00:12:14,159 --> 00:12:15,960
What do you want?

269
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:17,360
When I met Your Highness the first time,

270
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:19,320
I nearly died in the river.

271
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,960
For the second meeting,

272
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,600
I was just seeking to protect myself.

273
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:25,399
Both encounters

274
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,399
were beyond my control.

275
00:12:27,919 --> 00:12:29,440
So I wasn't trying to approach you.

276
00:12:33,180 --> 00:12:34,220
(Slave)

277
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:40,759
Though your arm bears a slave mark,

278
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:43,679
yet your behavior is neither humble
nor arrogant,

279
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:45,600
which is quite dignified.

280
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:48,399
You're no ordinary slave.

281
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:55,759
If Your Highness does not trust me,

282
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,840
then just set me free.

283
00:12:58,720 --> 00:13:00,519
You don't have to press me
so relentlessly.

284
00:13:04,559 --> 00:13:06,600
If I wish to keep someone,

285
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:11,360
they're not leaving alive.

286
00:13:21,279 --> 00:13:21,840
Your Highness?

287
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:27,399
Your Highness.

288
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:30,600
What did you do to the Princess?

289
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:32,200
You vile slave!

290
00:13:32,639 --> 00:13:33,960
I'll throw you in prison

291
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:34,960
and make you talk!

292
00:13:42,399 --> 00:13:43,000
Your Highness.

293
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:44,159
Ke'er.

294
00:13:47,639 --> 00:13:49,720
What did that slave do to you?

295
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:51,039
His background...

296
00:13:51,919 --> 00:13:53,240
How far have you investigated?

297
00:13:53,679 --> 00:13:55,039
He is indeed a registered slave.

298
00:13:55,559 --> 00:13:56,919
His entire family was registered
as deceased.

299
00:13:57,480 --> 00:13:58,399
No further leads.

300
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:01,159
We've been at war with Dongqing
for decades,

301
00:14:01,519 --> 00:14:02,720
and they plant spies constantly.

302
00:14:03,159 --> 00:14:06,320
Dongqing remnants
still abound at the border.

303
00:14:07,559 --> 00:14:08,720
After this battle,

304
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,279
your encounter with this man

305
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:11,960
could be a trap.

306
00:14:12,559 --> 00:14:13,919
If that's the case,

307
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:15,799
kill him

308
00:14:16,919 --> 00:14:18,320
to end future threats.
